This is a project for learning Japanese.
It is built on top of Next.js, TailwindCSS, and includes advanced features like:
- AI integration with LangChain, OpenAI, DeepSeek, and Ollama
- Database management with Prisma
- State management with React Query
- Type safety with tRPC and Zod
- Text-to-speech capabilities via Google Cloud or OpenAI
- Modern UI components with Heroicons and Geist
- UI styling with DaisyUI
- Code quality tools: ESLint, Prettier, and TypeScript
- PostCSS for CSS processing
